                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus from="1v" to="6r"/>
                           <desc type="GuestText">Introduction to the Miracles of Mary</desc>
                           <note>
                              The text is written in the same hand as <ref target="#a1"/>.
                              The note terminates as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">እስከ፡ አመ፡ ይመጽእ፡ በስብሐቲሁ፡ ወልደ፡ አሜን፡</q>.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus from="6r" to="7r"/>
                           <desc type="GuestText">Miracle of Mary</desc>
                           <note>
                              The text is written in the same hand as <ref target="#a1"/>.
                              The note begins as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">ተአምሪሃ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                              ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ በአኀቲ፡ ሀገር፡ ወሐልቁ፡ ብእሲቱ፡ ወደቂቁ፡</q>, and terminates as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">ወይቤሎሙ፡ ለሰብአ፡ ብሔሩ፡ ርእዩ፡ ዘረሰየተኒ፡ እግዝእት፡ ቅድስት፡
                                 ድንግል፡ ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ። ጸሎታ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                              </q>.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus from="7r" to="7v"/>
                           <desc type="GuestText">Miracle of Mary</desc>
                           <note>
                              The text is written in the same hand as <ref target="#a1"/>.
                              The note begins as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">ተአምሪሃ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                              ወሀሎ፡ ፩መነኮስ። ነዳይ፡ ዘአልቦቱ፡ ሲሳይ፨ ወአራዝ፡</q>, and terminates as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">ወአንከሩ፡ ኵሎሙ፨ እለ፡ ርእዩ፡ ወሰምኡ፡ ዘንተ፡ ተአምረ፡ ወመንክረ፡
                                 ዘገብረት፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፨ ማርያም። ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ። ጸሎታ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                              </q>.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                           <locus from="7v" to="8v"/>
                           <desc type="GuestText">
                              <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3633Miracle">Conversation of Jesus Christ and Our Lady Mary on the Five Pains</title>
                           </desc>
                           <note>
                              The text is written in the same hand as <ref target="#a1"/>.
                              The note begins as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">ተአምሪሃ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                              ወበአኂቱ፡ ዕለት፡ እመዋዕል፡ ይቤላ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ። ለወላዲቱ፡ ድንግል። ኦእምየ፡</q>, and terminates as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">አንቲ፡ ወአነ፡ ንመጽእ፡
                                 ኅቡረ፡ እምቅድመ፡ በ፫ዕለት፡ ወእንዘ፡ ዘንተ፡ ይትናገራ፨ እስመ፡ ሰምአ፡ ደቅስትዮስ፨፡ ውጸሐፈ፡ ከመ፡ ይጽሐፍዋ። ወያንብብዋ፡ ምዕመናን። ጸሎታ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                              </q>.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a6">
                           <locus target="#8v #106r"/>
                           <desc type="GuestText"><title cert="medium" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6205Saalnaka">Saʾalnāka maḥari saʾalnāka faṭāri saʾalnāka kahali</title>.</desc>
                           <note>
                              The text is written in the same hand as <ref target="#a1"/>.
                              The note begins as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">ሰአልናከ፡ መሐሪ፡ ሰአልናከ፡ ፈጣሪ፡ ሰአልናከ፡ ከሃሊ፡</q>, and terminates as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">አምዕዝ፡
                                 ለነ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘንተ፡ 
                                    <sic>ኅብስት፡</sic>
                                  ወዘንተ፡ ጽዋዓ፡ እስመ፡ 
                                    <sic>ኩሉ፡</sic>
                                  ዘጸውዓ፡ ስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡
                                 ይድኅን፡ 
                                    <sic>እምኩሉ፡</sic>
                                  መንሱት፡</q>.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                     </list>
